  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You can manifest the scaly toughness of dragonkind. Once per day as a swift action, you can harden your skin, giving it a scaly appearance and granting you DR 10/magic. During this time, you are also immune to paralysis and sleep effects. This effect lasts for a number of rounds equal to your oracle level.</p>\n<p>At 13th level, you can use this ability twice per day.</p>\n<p>You must be at least 7th level to select this revelation.</p>"
